            "title": "What Will Trump Say During Press Conference With Military? Crypto Prediction Market Is Wagering on These Words",
            "id": "0b387a65-e57c-4813-b1d4-7fb62dfb4bf6",
            "description": "Bettors in the cryptocurrency world are actively speculating on President Trump's upcoming conference with military officials. There is significant interest in whether the speech will be de-escalatory, with high stakes related to Trump mentioning \"Iran\" or \"Iranian\" over 15 times, having odds of 74% on Polymarket. The likelihood of Trump using words like \"Power\" or \"Strength\" stands at 85%, while terms such as \"Pilots/Crew/Staff\" have a 67% chance. Words such as \"Hell\" and \"Obliteration,\" previously used by Trump in reference to military actions in Iran, have odds of 69% and 65% respectively. The possibility of Trump mentioning \"Make a Deal\" is at 65%, but there are no bets placed on \"Ceasefire.\" The word-mention prediction market is seeing a surge in activity as Trump's speeches and conferences draw attention.",
